  <h1>About Moffat Bay Lodge</h1>
  <p>Welcome to Moffat Bay Lodge, a tranquil retreat nestled along the pristine shores of San Juan Islands. Our lodge offers a perfect escape for nature lovers, adventurers, and those looking to unwind in a peaceful setting.</p>
  
  <h2>Our Story</h2>
  <p>Moffat Bay Lodge was created with a vision to provide a sanctuary for guests to reconnect with nature. From its humble beginnings, the lodge has grown into a premier destination for those seeking a unique blend of rustic charm and modern comfort.</p>
  
  <h2>Amenities & Activities</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Spacious, comfortable cabins with breathtaking views of the bay</li>
    <li>Guided hiking trails through lush forests</li>
    <li>Water activities, including kayaking and fishing</li>
    <li>Outdoor fire pits for evening gatherings</li>
    <li>Dining facilities featuring locally-sourced ingredients</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
  <p>At Moffat Bay Lodge, we are dedicated to preserving the beauty of our natural surroundings while offering our guests an unforgettable experience. We believe in sustainable practices, supporting our local community, and providing exceptional service that keeps our guests returning year after year.</p>

  <p>We invite you to experience the magic of Moffat Bay Lodge and create memories that will last a lifetime.</p>
